reviewText: I ordered "The Best of Liberace Vol. 4"! The cover I got shows Vol. 4, inside was the disc Vol. 1 (I have that one already). The disc was full of scratches. And I  can't send the item back, because I live in Germany.
Bery entertaining.  It brught back many fond memories.  Enjoyed seeing guest stars from the past.  Highly recommend this dvd, even if you were not his fan.
